    <h4>20/01/08 - Hypernumbers Developers Alpha is released </h4>
    <p>We have begun the year as we plan to carry on, with software releases. On the right you 
    can download the latest release of a hypernumbers server.</p>

    <p>The tar.gz is a cross platform release that is tested on windows xp / vista, mac osx10 and 
        ubuntu, to get up and running check the README that comes with the download, or check the
        <a href="/docs/">documentation</a> (documentation will also be
        installed along side the hypernumbers server)</p>

    <p>Please post to the mailing list if you have any question or comments about this release. 
        We are interested in everyones views on hypernumbers and if there is any way we can help 
        you use hypernumbers to build something, tell us!</p>

